name: GLTCHPHT+SPHRINV+CNVRTD2LOFI_10MAKRO,2016
description: GLTCHPHT+SPHRINV+CNVRTD2LOFI_10MAKRO,2016 presents a hidden reality between manual and machine processing. Used a digital iPhone photography and glitched by analog and software tools the work transformed into a unique piece of art with a mirror effect and with highlighting the cell structure of the analog TV screen. This early work by Akhmadbaev is a part of the completed series of the images after processing in camera, scanner, PDF and analog converter tools.
